OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777539988
OL,3,CSmart electricity meter roll out from
OL,4,C2028 in NI homes
OL,6,FNew smart meters introduced to
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland in 2028 could help
OL,8,Fhomes and businesses save money on
OL,9,Ftheir electricity bills, Economy
OL,10,FMinister Caoimhe Archibald said.
OL,12,FA Smart Electricity Meters Design
OL,13,FPlan, published on Wednesday, outlines
OL,14,Fhow meters will be introduced in a
OL,15,F"carefully planned, consumer-focused
OL,16,Fway".
OL,18,FThe rollout, which will not involve
OL,19,Fupfront costs, is expected to begin at
OL,20,Fthe start of 2028 and will last three
OL,21,Fyears.
OL,26,@wD@AOUxD@DO]
