CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777539988
OL,3,CSmart electricity meter roll out from
OL,4,C2028 in NI homes
OL,6,FMs Archibald said smart meters will
OL,7,Freplace estimated bills and give
OL,8,Fpeople real-time information about how
OL,9,Fmuch electricity they use and when
OL,10,Fthey use it.
OL,12,FShe said the cost of energy and
OL,13,Fvolatile fuel prices driven by the war
OL,14,Fin Iran "is not fair and not
OL,15,Fsustainable" for homes and businesses.
OL,26,@vD@IOUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777539988
OL,3,CSmart electricity meter roll out from
OL,4,C2028 in NI homes
OL,6,F"Today's announcement marks an
OL,7,Fimportant step forward for the north,
OL,8,Fsupporting consumers to better manage
OL,9,Ftheir electricity usage and helping to
OL,10,Freduce electricity bills, as well as
OL,11,Fcreating greater resilience in our
OL,12,Flocal grid," she said.
OL,14,FTwo million smart meters are installed
OL,15,Facross the Republic of Ireland, and 22
OL,16,Fmillion smart meters are in use in
OL,17,FGreat Britain.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777539988
OL,3,CSmart electricity meter roll out from
OL,4,C2028 in NI homes
OL,6,FThe Department for the Economy said
OL,7,Fevidence shows that installed meters
OL,8,Fhad driven innovation and smarter
OL,9,Ftariffs from electricity suppliers
OL,10,Fwhich in turn significantly reduced
OL,11,Felectricity bills.
OL,13,FMs Archibald added: "The Design Plan
OL,14,Fpublished today sets out how smart
OL,15,Fmeters will be introduced here in a
OL,16,Fcarefully planned, consumer-focused
OL,17,Fway.
OL,26,@uD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777539988
OL,3,CSmart electricity meter roll out from
OL,4,C2028 in NI homes
OL,6,F"I'd like to reassure the public that
OL,7,Fthey do not have to do anything now.
OL,8,FNIE Networks and your electricity
OL,9,Fsupplier will be in touch at the right
OL,10,Ftime, and you will be supported
OL,11,Fthrough the process at every step.
OL,13,F"There will be no upfront cost for
OL,14,Finstallation, and no loss of choice.
OL,16,F"Fixed tariffs and prepayment options
OL,17,Fwill continue to be available, and
OL,18,Fsmart tariffs will be optional.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777539988
OL,3,CSmart electricity meter roll out from
OL,4,C2028 in NI homes
OL,6,F"This is about giving people better
OL,7,Finformation and ensuring that those
OL,8,Fwho are most vulnerable can choose to
OL,9,Freduce their electricity bills."
OL,11,FBusinesses, including small and medium
OL,12,Fsized firms, will also be covered by
OL,13,Fthe roll-out.
OL,15,FPat Austin, director of National
OL,16,FEnergy Action Northern Ireland, said:
OL,17,F"Smart meters can deliver real
OL,18,Fbenefits for households by helping
OL,19,Fpeople better understand their energy
OL,20,Fuse and avoid estimated bills.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@`O]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777539988
OL,3,CSmart electricity meter roll out from
OL,4,C2028 in NI homes
OL,6,F"A fair and inclusive rollout will be
OL,7,Fimportant to ensure vulnerable
OL,8,Fhouseholds can benefit from greater
OL,9,Fcontrol over their energy costs and
OL,10,Fenjoy warmer, healthier homes."
OL,12,FNoyona Chundur, chief executive of the
OL,13,FConsumer Council, said: "Smart meters
OL,14,Fwill help consumers better understand
OL,15,Fand manage their electricity use,
OL,16,Fsupporting informed choices that can
OL,17,Freduce bills and improve energy
OL,18,Fefficiency.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@_O]uD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/8
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
