OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777539988
OL,3,CSmart electricity meter roll out from
OL,4,C2028 in NI homes
OL,6,F"We welcome the Design Plan and will
OL,7,Fcontinue working with partners to
OL,8,Fensure strong consumer protections
OL,9,Fthroughout the rollout."
OL,11,FGemma McHale, head of smart metering
OL,12,Fat NIE Networks, added: "NIE Networks
OL,13,Fwelcomes publication of the Smart
OL,14,FElectricity Meters Design Plan.
OL,16,F"Smart meters will help deliver a more
OL,17,Fefficient electricity system and help
OL,18,Fcustomers get better value, and we
OL,19,Flook forward to working with partners
OL,20,Fto develop a robust programme and
OL,21,Fdelivery timeline."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@XO]tD@YOUxD@AOU}D@SO]
